CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Tuktu Resources Ltd. is a Canada-based junior oil and gas development company. The Company is engaged in producing oil and gas properties in southern Alberta. The Company's assets are located in southern Alberta consist of 29,685 gross hectares in southern Alberta near the Foothills County. The assets have a base production of approximately 165 barrels per day (bpd).
